OL,3,C'I'm almost in tears': Man meets staff
OL,4,Cwho saved his life
OL,6,FHe began CPR, or cardiopulmonary
OL,7,Fresuscitation, on Ray while the rest
OL,8,Fof the group phoned 999.
OL,10,FGreg said: "You're looking at one of
OL,11,Fyour best mates and you're just hoping
OL,12,Fand praying that he'll get over it.
OL,14,F"But the longer that time goes on and
OL,15,Fnothing happens, the more worried you
OL,16,Fstart to get."
