OL,3,C'I'm almost in tears': Man meets staff
OL,4,Cwho saved his life
OL,6,FHe added: "It's time critical and if
OL,7,Fyou don't start those chest
OL,8,Fcompressions, then for every minute
OL,9,Fthat goes by, your chances of recovery
OL,10,Fdrop by 10%."
OL,12,FRay said it felt like "someone turned
OL,13,Fa dimmer switch" and he did not
OL,14,Fremember much after.
OL,16,F"It was completely out of the blue. I
OL,17,Fjust started to feel fuzzy and my legs
OL,18,Ffelt heavy but there were not symptoms
OL,19,Fof a heart attack," he said.
