OL,3,C'I'm almost in tears': Man meets staff
OL,4,Cwho saved his life
OL,6,F"It was like someone turned a dimmer
OL,7,Fswitch and I didn't know anything
OL,8,Fafter that."
OL,10,FMedical crews were able to return
OL,11,FRay's heart rhythm and rushed him to
OL,12,FBroadgreen Hospital for further
OL,13,Ftreatment a short time later.
OL,15,FHe has now had a triple bypass
OL,16,Foperation and is on the road to
OL,17,Frecovery.
