OL,3,C'I'm almost in tears': Man meets staff
OL,4,Cwho saved his life
OL,6,FRay broke down in tears as he reunited
OL,7,Fwith the NWAS staff who saved him: "I
OL,8,Fdidn't see you at the time but my
OL,9,Ffriends told me what you were like."
OL,11,FPaula Rimmer, the NWAS paramedic who
OL,12,Fwas first on the scene, said that Ray
OL,13,F"had some great friends with him, who
OL,14,Fknew what to do on the day, they knew
OL,15,Fhow to raise the help nice and early,
OL,16,Fthey knew to start CPR."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
