OL,3,C'I'm almost in tears': Man meets staff
OL,4,Cwho saved his life
OL,6,F"The friends, without being asked,
OL,7,Fhelped to carry all of the kit and
OL,8,Fthey helped me across the fence so all
OL,9,Fthat meant that I could be at Ray's
OL,10,Fside a lot more quickly."
OL,12,FLauren O'Neill is an NWAS Apprentice
OL,13,FMedical Technician who also attended
OL,14,Fthe scene.
OL,16,FShe said: "It's lovely to actually
OL,17,Fhave a conversation with him and find
OL,18,Fout how he is doing and how his
OL,19,Frecovery has been. It reminds you why
OL,20,Fyou do the job and how it can really
OL,21,Faffect people's lives."
