OL,3,C'I'm almost in tears': Man meets staff
OL,4,Cwho saved his life
OL,6,FRay said: "I had never seen any of
OL,7,Fthem before. I missed a terrific day
OL,8,Fout. I thanked them very much and it
OL,9,Fis very difficult to know what to say
OL,10,Fother than 'thank you very much' and
OL,11,Fhug them."
OL,13,F"I was lucky to have a bunch of fellas
OL,14,Flike them around me, I mean, really
OL,15,Freally lucky."
